	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la">S[alutem] d[ico].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la">Valde me exhilaravit testimonium scholae <placeName ref="l2524">Scoticae</placeName> et fratrum in regno <placeName ref="l2524">Scotiae</placeName> Christum annunciantium confessioni nostrae exhibitum per publicum hoc instrumentum, quod mitto.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la">Volui enim et te et bonos isthic apud vos viros huius mei gaudii facere participes.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la">Ex <placeName ref="l822">Germania</placeName> nihil memoratu dignum adfertur, nisi quod principes Austriaci vivant in perquellis[?].</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la"><persName ref="p8282">Maximilianus</persName> dicitur festinare <placeName ref="l396">Pragam</placeName>, ut auxilia petat et exactiones instituat.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la">Ita <persName ref="p18477">Ferdinandus</persName> in comitatum <placeName ref="l777">Tyrolensem</placeName> est profectus.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la">Vix supterfugiet <placeName ref="l862">Helvetia</placeName>; reposcetur et illa, suppetias contra <placeName ref="l2510">Turcam</placeName> ferat, misceat se bello non necessario.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Ohne Adresse.]<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><hi>Datum, Unterschrift und Adresse wurden vom Abschreiber durch einen Vermerk am Briefanfang ersetzt:</hi> Idem eidem. <placeName ref="l587">Tiguro</placeName> <placeName ref="l41">Bernam</placeName>. 20. decembris 1566.</note></note>
				</p>
			</div>
